{"tid":1274693,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得今次71係一場警察對傳媒大眾既show","createTime":"2019-07-01T17:07:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T18:29:55.000Z","uid":5956,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7f9f6208c4d764113d314815a595768131961f30","tid":1274693,"uid":5956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:07:10.000Z","msg":"首先，今次衝立法會，得20幾個警犬去守，任意去俾示威者輕易入去<br />\n<br />\n其次，係10點半，警犬係Facebook 岀post, 話會清場。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一，係69 612，兩次咁耐以黎，都冇係Facebook 話俾你知會清場(大慨既時間都冇),每次岀facebook post都係話強烈譴責，話會用適當嘅武力驅散示威者，時間上已經冇說明過會有確實時間清場<br />\n<br />\n第二，頭先已經有po 話過PPRB 個高級警犬隻錶show 個時間係5點，代表條片已經預先錄好等播岀街<br />\n<br />\n第三，係69 612事件入面，清場個陣幾可有見過班防暴會舉起3支黑旗俾啱啱清場既示威者睇<br />\n<br />\n第四，速龍個班係612，又對記者講記你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，又追打示威者，點解今晚會冇呢d情況岀現？而且頭先係直播見到有個速龍想衝，但俾第二個速龍禁住唔好衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">劇本係呢度: <a href=\"https://zh-yue.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/大事件\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh-yue.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6&d=qB%2BEr1lTQcBPVU2CyFsNooRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=4c860b96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh-yue.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/大事件</a> </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以今次唔係做media show 我係唔撚信既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"a04e7e5508702baa224dba37be012e277a450aa3","tid":1274693,"uid":5956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:10:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f088a6b8791f09b7933e5e987